                      "children": [
                        {
                          "text": "official portal"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "Step 2: ",
                      "bold": true
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Navigate to the “ONLINE PORTAL FOR TAD EDUCATIONAL INCENTIVE SCHEMES” on the homepage."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "Step 3:",
                      "bold": true
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " Upload the application form along with the required documents before the notified deadline."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "Post Application Process:",
                      "bold": true,
                      "underline": true,
                      "italic": true
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "bold": true,
                      "text": "Step 1:"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " The college will verify the online applications and forward them to the respective sanctioning authorities (TAD Project Officer / CEO, Zila Parishad)."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "Step 2: ",
                      "bold": true
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Sanctioning authorities will approve the verified applications online. Incomplete applications, if any, will be returned for correction."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "Step 3:",
                      "bold": true
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " Approved applications will be sent to the district treasury office for disbursement."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "Step 4:",
                      "bold": true
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " The sanctioned amount will be transferred directly to the student's bank account linked with their Bhamashah card."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "process_md": "**Step 1:** Eligible students must fill out the prescribed application form online via the [official portal](https://tad.rajasthan.gov.in/services/136).\n**Step 2:** Navigate to the “ONLINE PORTAL FOR TAD EDUCATIONAL INCENTIVE SCHEMES” on the homepage.\n**Step 3:** Upload the application form along with the required documents before the notified deadline.\n***Post Application Process:***\n**Step 1:** The college will verify the online applications and forward them to the respective sanctioning authorities (TAD Project Officer / CEO, Zila Parishad).\n**Step 2:** Sanctioning authorities will approve the verified applications online. Incomplete applications, if any, will be returned for correction.\n**Step 3:** Approved applications will be sent to the district treasury office for disbursement.\n**Step 4:** The sanctioned amount will be transferred directly to the student&amp;#39;s bank account linked with their Bhamashah card.\n"
        }
