      "schemeDefinitions": [],
      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant should be studying regularly a undergraduate or postgraduate course in a government college.\n1. The student should belong to a Scheduled Tribe community residing in the Scheduled Areas of Rajasthan. \n1. The applicant should be a native of Rajasthan.\n1. The applicant should be studying in a government college.\n1. The applicant should not be residing in a government-run hostel.\n1. The applicant&#39;s parents/guardian/husband should not be an income tax payer.\n1. The applicant should not have any academic gap (break) after passing the last board examination.\n1. The applicant should possess a valid Bhamashah card and an Aadhaar card.\n\n",
